title: 245: Are the Eagles still the NFC Favorites?
itunes:title: 245: Are the Eagles still the NFC Favorites?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Lance Zierlein preview the return of Aaron Rodgers (1:46), debate if the Eagles are still the conference favorite (21:03) and pick their game of the week between the Steelers and Patriots (7:22). The guys also highlight a few breakout rookies (22:57) and pick the early bowl matchups (34:11).
